<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>포인트 샵</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style/pointshop_style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="shop-container">
    <h2 class="shop-title">🎁 포인트 샵</h2>

    <div class="point-info">
      안녕하세요, <strong><%= user.user_id %></strong>님 <br>
      현재 보유 포인트: <strong><%= user.point %>P</strong>
    </div>

    <div class="item-list">
      <div class="item">
        <h4>☕ 학교 카페 쿠폰</h4>
        <p>아메리카노 1잔 / 300P</p>
        <form action="/pointshop/buy" method="POST">
          <input type="hidden" name="item" value="cafe_coupon">
          <button type="submit">구매하기</button>
        </form>
      </div>

      <div class="item">
        <h4>🍚 학식 쿠폰</h4>
        <p>1회 이용권 / 400P</p>
        <form action="/pointshop/buy" method="POST">
          <input type="hidden" name="item" value="meal_coupon">
          <button type="submit">구매하기</button>
        </form>
      </div>

      <div class="item">
        <h4>🎉 기프티콘</h4>
        <p>기프티콘 / 500P</p>
        <form action="/pointshop/buy" method="POST">
          <input type="hidden" name="item" value="gifticon">
          <button type="submit">구매하기</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a href="/">다시 돌아가기</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>